WEBVTT

00:06.615 --> 00:08.617
Let's meet the man.

00:08.660 --> 00:10.445
[Knocking]

00:10.488 --> 00:19.454
♪

00:19.497 --> 00:20.672
[Door opens]

00:20.716 --> 00:27.375
♪

00:27.418 --> 00:29.464
Pissing our pants yet?

00:29.507 --> 00:34.556
♪

00:34.599 --> 00:39.126
Boy, do I have a feeling
we're getting close.

00:39.169 --> 00:42.738
The post-apocalyptic world
is full of heroes and villains.

00:42.781 --> 00:51.225
♪

00:51.268 --> 00:54.663
Most of the time,
those lines are blurred.

00:54.706 --> 00:56.186
♪

00:56.230 --> 00:58.362
Negan: I did what I had to do
back then.

00:58.406 --> 01:01.017
♪

01:01.061 --> 01:03.628
I made myself into a monster

01:03.672 --> 01:07.284
because that is what
the world needed.

01:07.328 --> 01:11.245
♪

01:11.288 --> 01:13.551
We're all heroes
of our own stories.

01:13.595 --> 01:15.597
♪

01:15.640 --> 01:17.294
Now, if you look
at Negan's journey

01:17.338 --> 01:20.123
from a different point of view,

01:20.167 --> 01:22.473
well, it might change
how you feel about him.

01:22.517 --> 01:23.605
♪

01:23.648 --> 01:26.434
Little pig, little pig,

01:26.477 --> 01:29.001
let me in!

01:29.045 --> 01:30.742
Here is Negan's story.

01:30.786 --> 01:40.143
♪

01:40.187 --> 01:49.544
♪

01:49.587 --> 01:58.596
♪

01:58.640 --> 02:00.816
Negan: Well, I hope you got
your shitting pants on, boy,

02:00.859 --> 02:04.036
'cause you are about
to shit your pants.

02:04.080 --> 02:08.432
Before the world went to hell,
Negan was a regular guy.

02:08.476 --> 02:12.044
Please tell me
that you did not spend $600

02:12.088 --> 02:13.872
on this
"Happy Days" bullshit.

02:13.916 --> 02:16.701
He may not have been the best
husband, but I'll say this.

02:16.745 --> 02:19.182
He did love his wife, Lucille.

02:19.226 --> 02:20.836
[Door opens]

02:20.879 --> 02:25.841
But then Lucille,
she got devastating news.

02:25.884 --> 02:29.758
What's going on?

02:29.801 --> 02:31.194
What is it?

02:31.238 --> 02:38.810
♪

02:38.854 --> 02:41.422
I've got cancer.

02:41.465 --> 02:44.425
And then everyone
got devastating news.

02:44.468 --> 02:47.602
[Engine starts]Man: ...and Cumberland have
concluded that in all cases,

02:47.645 --> 02:49.038
the killers are eating
the flesh

02:49.081 --> 02:50.431
of the people they kill.

02:50.474 --> 02:53.216
Morgan: All of a sudden,
people started dying

02:53.260 --> 02:56.393
and coming back from the dead.

02:56.437 --> 02:59.309
Lucille, her cancer diagnosis

02:59.353 --> 03:02.182
was
a personal apocalypse for Negan.

03:02.225 --> 03:05.750
He became less selfish,
a better man.

03:05.794 --> 03:08.492
Caring for his wife
gave him purpose.

03:08.536 --> 03:16.283
♪

03:16.326 --> 03:18.241
Until one morning
when their world

03:18.285 --> 03:20.200
was turned upside down again.

03:22.376 --> 03:25.683
No, no, no, no, no, no,
no, no, no, no.

03:25.727 --> 03:33.300
♪

03:33.343 --> 03:40.655
♪

03:40.698 --> 03:45.790
Determined to save his wife,
he hatched a plan.

03:45.834 --> 03:49.968
We have made it this far, so we
are gonna see this through.

03:50.012 --> 03:53.276
I'm gonna find these doctors,
and I am gonna bring you back

03:53.320 --> 03:55.496
the drugs that you need,

03:55.539 --> 03:58.890
and we are gonna kick
this cancer out of you.

03:58.934 --> 04:00.283
[Sobbing]

04:00.327 --> 04:06.376
♪

04:06.420 --> 04:08.726
He finds the people
he's heard rumors about.

04:08.770 --> 04:11.207
♪

04:11.251 --> 04:13.165
[Sighs]

04:13.209 --> 04:15.429
Drop your guns!
Drop your guns!

04:15.472 --> 04:17.039
I don't want to shoot him,
but I will.

04:17.082 --> 04:19.868
Okay. Take it easy.

04:19.911 --> 04:24.525
Morgan:
Although he might not make
the best first impression.

04:24.568 --> 04:26.788
♪

04:26.831 --> 04:27.919
No, don't.

04:27.963 --> 04:28.920
♪

04:28.964 --> 04:29.921
[Thud]

04:29.965 --> 04:35.318
♪

04:35.362 --> 04:37.973
But they eventually come around.

04:38.016 --> 04:39.627
♪

04:39.670 --> 04:41.542
I found
that note you wrote.

04:41.585 --> 04:43.021
My daughter
went out to the warehouse

04:43.065 --> 04:44.980
to see
if we have what you need.

04:45.023 --> 04:49.550
[Door opens]

04:49.593 --> 04:50.899
[Door closes]

04:50.942 --> 04:52.509
We had it all.

04:52.553 --> 04:55.382
Everything on your list.

04:55.425 --> 04:57.384
I don't know what to say here.
Um...

04:57.427 --> 05:00.735
We have a lot.
We just want to help.

05:00.778 --> 05:03.868
They not only gave him
the medicine that he needs,

05:03.912 --> 05:07.785
but they also give him one
bad-ass way to defend himself.

05:07.829 --> 05:09.439
♪

05:09.483 --> 05:11.659
There's a gang that owns
the roads at night

05:11.702 --> 05:13.965
Is that empty gun
your only weapon?

05:14.009 --> 05:17.012
Yeah, I broke my hammer
on the way here.

05:19.057 --> 05:21.973
Here. Take this.

05:22.017 --> 05:24.236
This the bat
you hit me with?

05:24.280 --> 05:26.848
♪

05:26.891 --> 05:28.850
Damn, girl.

05:28.893 --> 05:31.200
You pack a wallop.

05:31.243 --> 05:34.464
♪

05:34.508 --> 05:36.597
Morgan:
On his way back to his wife,

05:36.640 --> 05:41.297
Negan gets captured by the same
gang he was warned about.

05:41.341 --> 05:43.038
You gotta let me go.

05:43.081 --> 05:46.084
♪

05:46.128 --> 05:48.609
Negan is forced to give up
information about the folks

05:48.652 --> 05:50.524
who just had helped him.

05:50.567 --> 05:53.091
If you don't start talking
by the time I stop,

05:53.135 --> 05:55.267
I swear to God...Wait, wait, wait.

05:55.311 --> 05:56.921
Just bring me my map.

05:56.965 --> 05:58.445
[Sighs]

05:58.488 --> 06:00.055
Bring me my map.

06:00.098 --> 06:06.496
♪

06:06.540 --> 06:09.412
He doesn't want to, but he
doesn't see another way out.

06:09.456 --> 06:11.632
He has to get back to his wife.

06:11.675 --> 06:14.025
♪

06:14.069 --> 06:16.071
However, nothing could have
prepared him

06:16.114 --> 06:18.073
for what he saw
when he got home.

06:18.116 --> 06:23.078
♪

06:23.121 --> 06:25.080
[Growling]

06:28.257 --> 06:30.477
[Growling]

06:30.520 --> 06:34.916
♪

06:34.959 --> 06:36.700
[Crying]

06:36.744 --> 06:44.447
♪

06:44.491 --> 06:46.318
He couldn't save Lucille.

06:46.362 --> 06:49.844
♪

06:49.887 --> 06:51.846
[Growling]

06:51.889 --> 06:56.633
♪

06:56.677 --> 06:59.027
So when he lost Lucille,

06:59.070 --> 07:02.683
there was no longer a reason
to keep a lid on his rage.

07:02.726 --> 07:07.905
♪

07:07.949 --> 07:12.475
♪

07:12.519 --> 07:13.520
[Negan grunts]

07:13.563 --> 07:15.870
And unfortunately
for those guys...

07:15.913 --> 07:21.266
♪

07:21.310 --> 07:23.225
[Groaning]

07:23.268 --> 07:26.097
...Negan had no reason
to spare them.

07:26.141 --> 07:28.535
Negan:
Now when I see red,

07:28.578 --> 07:32.713
it's just a question
of what I am capable of.

07:32.756 --> 07:36.412
And, well, man,
I hate to break it to ya.

07:36.456 --> 07:37.718
See, I am starting to think

07:37.761 --> 07:42.113
that I am capable
of damn near anything.

07:42.157 --> 07:46.074
♪

07:46.117 --> 07:50.165
So this...

07:50.208 --> 07:52.733
this is for not killing me.

07:52.776 --> 07:55.823
♪

07:55.866 --> 07:59.783
[Walkers growling]

07:59.827 --> 08:01.829
After a while,
after some trial and error,

08:01.872 --> 08:06.964
Negan found himself as a leader
of a community, the Sanctuary,

08:07.008 --> 08:10.620
and from the start,
he did it his way.

08:10.664 --> 08:15.538
So you kill the right people
at the right time...

08:15.582 --> 08:18.193
♪

08:18.236 --> 08:22.284
...everything falls
into place,

08:22.327 --> 08:25.026
everybody's happy.

08:25.069 --> 08:26.854
Well...

08:26.897 --> 08:30.292
some people more than others.

08:30.335 --> 08:33.556
But you kill one,

08:33.600 --> 08:35.689
and you could be saving
hundreds more,

08:35.732 --> 08:39.997
and that is what
we are all about.

08:40.041 --> 08:41.825
We save people.

08:41.869 --> 08:44.480
He solidified
his leadership by commanding

08:44.524 --> 08:47.048
an almost cult-like following.

08:47.091 --> 08:50.225
Until one day his men
came across some folks

08:50.268 --> 08:54.621
led by an ex-sheriff
by the name of Rick Grimes.

08:54.664 --> 08:56.057
And those people,

08:56.100 --> 08:58.233
well, they didn't
want to play by the rules.

08:58.276 --> 09:02.411
♪

09:02.454 --> 09:06.284
They attacked Negan's people.

09:06.328 --> 09:11.246
Was Negan in that building
last night, or was he here?

09:11.289 --> 09:12.595
Both.

09:12.639 --> 09:14.684
♪

09:14.728 --> 09:16.817
I'm Negan, shithead.

09:16.860 --> 09:18.819
♪

09:18.862 --> 09:21.604
Now, there's a whole world
of fun that we can talk about,

09:21.648 --> 09:22.866
so let's have a chat.

09:22.910 --> 09:24.128
I'm sorry it had
to come to this.

09:24.172 --> 09:26.348
[Gunshot]

09:26.391 --> 09:28.306
Big mistake, Rick.

09:28.350 --> 09:31.832
Big mistake.

09:31.875 --> 09:33.834
♪

09:33.877 --> 09:38.099
[Whistling]

09:38.142 --> 09:40.014
Go! Go!

09:40.057 --> 09:45.497
♪

09:45.541 --> 09:47.674
[Whistling continues]

09:47.717 --> 09:50.111
♪

09:50.154 --> 09:52.504
[Group whistling]

09:52.548 --> 09:57.727
♪

09:57.771 --> 10:01.209
You made it. Welcome
to where you're going.

10:01.252 --> 10:03.690
♪

10:03.733 --> 10:07.041
All right,
let's meet the man.

10:07.084 --> 10:14.483
♪

10:14.526 --> 10:19.923
♪

10:19.967 --> 10:24.232
Hi. You're Rick, right?

10:24.275 --> 10:26.060
I'm Negan.

10:26.103 --> 10:29.237
♪

10:29.280 --> 10:32.893
You are so gonna regret
crossing me in a few minutes.

10:32.936 --> 10:35.547
♪

10:35.591 --> 10:37.811
And with that,

10:37.854 --> 10:42.163
Negan and Rick, well,
they finally meet face to face.

10:42.206 --> 10:45.732
I don't want
to kill you people.

10:45.775 --> 10:48.212
I want you to work for me.

10:48.256 --> 10:52.564
You can't do that
if you're dead, now can you?

10:52.608 --> 10:54.871
♪

10:54.915 --> 10:58.135
But you killed my people,

10:58.179 --> 11:01.922
and for that -- For that,
you're gonna pay.

11:01.965 --> 11:06.230
Eenie...

11:06.274 --> 11:08.319
meenie...

11:08.363 --> 11:11.148
miney...

11:11.192 --> 11:12.280
mo.

11:12.323 --> 11:17.938
♪

11:17.981 --> 11:19.766
[Woman screams]

11:19.809 --> 11:20.723
♪

11:20.767 --> 11:22.029
[Negan grunts, thud]

11:22.072 --> 11:24.161
Morgan:
After Negan kills Abraham,

11:24.205 --> 11:26.860
Rick's right-hand man,
Daryl,

11:26.903 --> 11:29.993
he goes and does
something extra stupid...

11:30.037 --> 11:33.605
♪

11:33.649 --> 11:37.392
...and has to pay the price.

11:37.435 --> 11:38.610
♪

11:38.654 --> 11:42.353
That is a no-no.

11:42.397 --> 11:44.007
Back to it.

11:44.051 --> 11:47.619
♪

11:47.663 --> 11:49.404
Woman: No!

11:49.447 --> 11:52.450
Now, Negan doesn't want to keep
killing these guys.

11:52.494 --> 11:55.410
He's just trying to
teach them his rules.

11:55.453 --> 11:59.980
♪

12:00.023 --> 12:02.722
And after they finally
start getting the picture,

12:02.765 --> 12:07.248
Negan returns to the Sanctuary
with Daryl as his prisoner.

12:07.291 --> 12:10.468
Ha ha ha!
Dwighty Boy!

12:10.512 --> 12:13.515
He sees value
in strong people like Daryl.

12:13.558 --> 12:18.650
He wants him to be like Dwight,
one of Negan's top lieutenants.

12:18.694 --> 12:21.088
And this Dwight guy,
he is still loyal,

12:21.131 --> 12:23.177
despite getting half of his face
burned off

12:23.220 --> 12:26.354
and being forced to give up
his wife to Negan.

12:26.397 --> 12:30.271
♪

12:30.314 --> 12:32.273
[Chuckles]

12:32.316 --> 12:36.016
After giving Daryl some time
to think about his options --

12:36.059 --> 12:39.106
die in a cell eating dog food
or work for Negan --

12:39.149 --> 12:40.803
he pays him a visit.

12:40.847 --> 12:45.068
This, well...

12:45.112 --> 12:48.506
it can all be yours.

12:48.550 --> 12:50.857
All you gotta do

12:50.900 --> 12:55.818
is answer
one simple question.

12:55.862 --> 13:02.259
♪

13:02.303 --> 13:05.872
Who are you?

13:05.915 --> 13:09.266
Daryl.

13:09.310 --> 13:12.879
But that Daryl,
he is a stubborn one.

13:12.922 --> 13:14.315
[Cell door clangs]

13:14.358 --> 13:16.752
So Negan brings him
along on a field trip

13:16.796 --> 13:18.710
to see his old friend Rick.

13:18.754 --> 13:21.539
Little pig, little pig...

13:21.583 --> 13:23.977
let me in!

13:24.020 --> 13:27.197
Now, when the Saviors
meet a new community,

13:27.241 --> 13:30.548
they take half the crap.
That's just the way it is.

13:30.592 --> 13:33.856
But that Rick, he still doesn't
quite get how things work.

13:33.900 --> 13:38.774
Youdon't decide
what we take.

13:38.818 --> 13:39.906
Ido.

13:39.949 --> 13:42.473
Satisfied with their haul,

13:42.517 --> 13:45.781
Negan and the Saviors
head back to Sanctuary.

13:45.825 --> 13:48.915
And all is well...

13:48.958 --> 13:51.091
until he's paid
a surprise visit.

13:51.134 --> 13:53.180
Stay back!
Drop your weapons!

13:53.223 --> 13:55.660
I only want Negan.

13:55.704 --> 13:57.749
He killed my friends.

13:57.793 --> 13:59.795
No one else needs to die.

13:59.839 --> 14:01.318
[Machine-gun fire]

14:01.362 --> 14:06.976
♪

14:07.020 --> 14:11.024
And Negan, he likes what he sees
in this kid.

14:11.067 --> 14:13.156
Is that any way to treat
our new guest?

14:13.200 --> 14:14.331
[Walkers growling]

14:14.375 --> 14:16.943
So he shows him
around the place.

14:19.859 --> 14:22.600
So, do I kill you?

14:22.644 --> 14:24.646
Iron your face?

14:24.689 --> 14:26.909
Chop off your arm?

14:26.953 --> 14:32.132
Tell me.
What do you think?

14:32.175 --> 14:33.742
I think you jump out
the window to save me

14:33.785 --> 14:35.570
the trouble
of killing you.

14:35.613 --> 14:37.920
[Chuckles] Oh.

14:37.964 --> 14:40.009
Ohh!

14:40.053 --> 14:44.187
Now, there is the kid that
impressed the hell out of me.

14:44.231 --> 14:46.189
♪

14:46.233 --> 14:48.757
Let's go for a ride, kid.

14:48.800 --> 14:50.585
♪

14:50.628 --> 14:54.981
Negan brings Carl back
to Alexandria safe and sound,

14:55.024 --> 14:56.808
and with Rick out on a run,
well,

14:56.852 --> 14:58.854
Negan makes himself at home.

14:58.898 --> 15:01.030
Damn, that smells good.

15:01.074 --> 15:03.990
And life is really good
in the suburbs.

15:04.033 --> 15:08.429
You should know
that Rick Grimes

15:08.472 --> 15:11.127
has a history of
not working well with others.

15:11.171 --> 15:14.870
You know,
I'm thinking, Spencer.

15:14.914 --> 15:17.220
I'm thinking
how Rick threatened to kill me,

15:17.264 --> 15:20.571
how he clearly hates my guts.

15:20.615 --> 15:24.053
But he is out there
right now

15:24.097 --> 15:26.664
gathering shit
for me to make sure

15:26.708 --> 15:31.495
I don't hurt any of
the fine people that live here.

15:31.539 --> 15:33.410
And then there's you...

15:33.454 --> 15:36.022
♪

15:36.065 --> 15:38.154
...the guy who waited for Rick
to be gone

15:38.198 --> 15:39.634
so he could sneak over

15:39.677 --> 15:42.028
and talk to me
to get me to do his dirty work

15:42.071 --> 15:44.900
so he could take
Rick's place.

15:44.944 --> 15:49.644
You know what I'm thinking?
'Cause I have a guess.

15:49.687 --> 15:51.994
♪

15:52.038 --> 15:57.043
It's because
you got no guts.

15:57.086 --> 15:58.435
♪

15:58.479 --> 15:59.567
[Gasps]

15:59.610 --> 16:05.703
♪

16:05.747 --> 16:07.879
[Gunshot]

16:07.923 --> 16:09.272
Shit!

16:09.316 --> 16:10.447
♪

16:10.491 --> 16:12.667
Despite the attempt
on his life,

16:12.710 --> 16:16.627
Negan always recognizes
opportunity when he sees it.

16:16.671 --> 16:18.847
♪

16:18.890 --> 16:21.284
What is this?

16:21.328 --> 16:24.157
This was homemade.

16:24.200 --> 16:28.030
And while Negan tries to find
out who the bullet maker is,

16:28.074 --> 16:31.425
Rick finally returns.

16:31.468 --> 16:33.688
Your shit's waiting for you
at the gate.

16:33.731 --> 16:36.691
Just go.

16:36.734 --> 16:39.259
Sure thing, Rick.

16:39.302 --> 16:45.656
Right after I find the guy
or gal that made this bullet.

16:45.700 --> 16:46.962
♪

16:47.006 --> 16:48.529
It was me.

16:48.572 --> 16:50.487
[Sobbing]

16:50.531 --> 16:51.967
It was only me.

16:52.011 --> 16:56.058
All in all,
it was a very successful trip.

16:56.102 --> 17:00.541
Negan reminded the Alexandrians
who was in charge

17:00.584 --> 17:05.328
and got a fancy new bullet maker
with a mullet.

17:05.372 --> 17:07.026
♪

17:07.069 --> 17:11.552
But back at the Sanctuary,
there's less pleasant news.

17:11.595 --> 17:13.728
Daryl has escaped.

17:16.122 --> 17:18.385
So while his men go searching,

17:18.428 --> 17:21.997
Negan calls up
his newest recruit.

17:22.041 --> 17:25.174
Hey.

17:25.218 --> 17:30.092
You do not need to be
scared anymore.

17:30.136 --> 17:34.096
You don't need to be scared.

17:34.140 --> 17:37.926
You just have to answer me
one question.

17:37.969 --> 17:39.319
And it's a big one.

17:39.362 --> 17:41.756
♪

17:41.799 --> 17:44.976
Who are...
I'm Negan.

17:45.020 --> 17:50.243
I'm utterly, completely,
stone-cold Negan.

17:50.286 --> 17:52.245
I was Negan
before I even met you.

17:52.288 --> 17:55.422
I just needed to meet you
properly to know.

17:55.465 --> 17:57.032
But not everyone in Rick's group

17:57.076 --> 17:59.643
is as eager to join
the Saviors.

17:59.687 --> 18:03.604
[Amplified] Hello.

18:03.647 --> 18:05.214
I come salved with the hope

18:05.258 --> 18:07.564
that it is my dropped
knowledge that you heed.

18:07.608 --> 18:10.437
Options are zero to none.

18:10.480 --> 18:13.266
Compliance and fealty
are your only escape.

18:13.309 --> 18:16.007
Where's Negan?

18:16.051 --> 18:19.924
Rick, he thinks he's got
the upper hand.

18:19.968 --> 18:23.276
I'm Negan.

18:23.319 --> 18:28.019
Rick finds out his allies
are working for Negan,

18:28.063 --> 18:29.586
and Negan's not done.

18:29.630 --> 18:31.632
See, he's got another card
to play.

18:31.675 --> 18:34.330
So you don't like Eugene
anymore.

18:34.374 --> 18:36.767
♪

18:36.811 --> 18:41.424
You guys
gotta like Sasha.

18:41.468 --> 18:43.165
I do, too.

18:43.209 --> 18:46.255
♪

18:46.299 --> 18:49.476
Got her right here,
packaged for your convenience.

18:49.519 --> 18:52.218
I want all the guns
you've managed to scrape up.

18:52.261 --> 18:55.395
And I want it now,

18:55.438 --> 18:57.048
or Sasha dies.

18:57.092 --> 18:59.442
Let me see her.

18:59.486 --> 19:02.663
♪

19:02.706 --> 19:04.621
Oh.

19:04.665 --> 19:07.494
All right.
Just give me a second.

19:07.537 --> 19:09.235
I might have to get her
up to speed.

19:09.278 --> 19:13.326
You can't hear shit
inside this thing.

19:13.369 --> 19:17.243
Everything was going
according to plan.

19:17.286 --> 19:19.070
You're not gonna believe
this crap.

19:19.114 --> 19:21.638
[Growling]
Holy goddamn!

19:21.682 --> 19:28.863
♪

19:28.906 --> 19:32.040
♪

19:32.083 --> 19:35.217
Ah, honey, God damn it.

19:35.261 --> 19:36.653
[Growling]

19:36.697 --> 19:39.700
But that's why you always have
a plan B.

19:39.743 --> 19:42.703
We can make another deal.

19:42.746 --> 19:45.532
[Gunshot]
Aah!

19:45.575 --> 19:49.492
And Rick finds himself
on his knees in front of Negan.

19:49.536 --> 19:50.798
Again.

19:50.841 --> 19:54.236
♪

19:54.280 --> 19:58.327
I guess I got to start
all over again.

19:59.676 --> 20:03.289
I truly don't know what more
I could have done to warn you.

20:03.332 --> 20:05.421
And this isn't a warning.

20:05.465 --> 20:08.076
This is punishment.

20:08.119 --> 20:09.947
♪

20:09.991 --> 20:13.516
I'm gonna kill Carl now.

20:13.560 --> 20:19.305
I'm gonna make it
one nice, hard swing.

20:19.348 --> 20:24.658
Try to do it in one
because I like him.

20:24.701 --> 20:26.703
I just want you to put that
in your brain

20:26.747 --> 20:28.792
and roll it around
for a minute.

20:28.836 --> 20:33.275
I'm gonna kill Carl,
and then Lucille here,

20:33.319 --> 20:36.539
she's gonna take
your hands.

20:36.583 --> 20:39.412
♪

20:39.455 --> 20:42.066
You can do it
right in front of me.

20:42.110 --> 20:45.548
You can take my hands.

20:45.592 --> 20:51.598
I told you already --
I'm gonna kill you.

20:51.641 --> 20:54.165
All of you.

20:54.209 --> 20:55.732
Okay.

20:55.776 --> 21:02.043
♪

21:02.086 --> 21:04.219
You said I can do it.

21:04.263 --> 21:05.525
[Growling]

21:05.568 --> 21:07.178
[Screaming]

21:07.222 --> 21:08.528
[Gunfire]

21:08.571 --> 21:14.795
♪

21:14.838 --> 21:17.450
He's given Rick's group
multiple chances,

21:17.493 --> 21:20.975
but now, see,
Negan is done playing around.

21:21.018 --> 21:27.590
♪

21:27.634 --> 21:33.988
♪

21:34.031 --> 21:37.383
So I'm not exactly feeling
a reason for us

21:37.426 --> 21:41.256
to try throwing lead
at each other.

21:41.300 --> 21:44.607
You're gonna
make me count.

21:44.651 --> 21:46.348
[Scoffs lightly]

21:46.392 --> 21:49.569
Okay, okay.

21:49.612 --> 21:51.788
I'm counting.

21:51.832 --> 21:54.182
10...

21:54.225 --> 21:56.184
9...

21:56.227 --> 21:58.578
8...

21:58.621 --> 22:00.754
7...

22:00.797 --> 22:02.625
[Gun cocks]

22:02.669 --> 22:09.806
♪

22:09.850 --> 22:17.292
♪

22:17.336 --> 22:20.513
Now, Rick may have decimated
the Sanctuary,

22:20.556 --> 22:22.993
but he missed
his primary target.

22:23.037 --> 22:25.692
♪

22:25.735 --> 22:28.999
And Negan, he decides it's time

22:29.043 --> 22:31.872
to take the fight
back to Alexandria.

22:31.915 --> 22:34.657
[Gunfire]

22:34.701 --> 22:39.880
♪

22:39.923 --> 22:43.144
I'm gonna go to Rick's,
make a little spaghetti.

22:43.187 --> 22:45.494
When he shows up,
send him my way.

22:45.538 --> 22:49.063
And he wants Ricks...

22:49.106 --> 22:50.804
all for himself.

22:50.847 --> 22:55.069
♪

22:55.112 --> 22:56.766
Michonne.

22:56.810 --> 22:59.116
♪

22:59.160 --> 23:01.075
[Grunts]

23:01.118 --> 23:04.295
♪

23:04.339 --> 23:06.515
This shit
isn't funny anymore.

23:06.559 --> 23:08.169
Aah!

23:08.212 --> 23:10.519
[Breathing heavily]

23:10.563 --> 23:13.348
Don't make me do this now,
Rick.

23:13.392 --> 23:15.829
I got plans for you.

23:15.872 --> 23:17.526
Cut you
in little bitty pieces,

23:17.570 --> 23:19.223
feed you to the dead,
and make you watch.

23:19.267 --> 23:20.921
Aah! Aah!

23:20.964 --> 23:22.705
You ever shut the hell up?

23:22.749 --> 23:23.880
Nope.

23:23.924 --> 23:27.362
♪

23:27.406 --> 23:29.320
[Muffled] Aah!
Don't you touch her!

23:29.364 --> 23:31.497
[Grunts]

23:31.540 --> 23:32.889
[Lucille thuds]

23:32.933 --> 23:39.243
♪

23:39.287 --> 23:42.986
[Screams]

23:43.030 --> 23:44.945
Rick is a slippery one, and he,

23:44.988 --> 23:48.427
along with most of his group,
they manage to escape,

23:48.470 --> 23:50.472
so Negan makes it back
to the Sanctuary,

23:50.516 --> 23:53.475
only to find out
that his top guy

23:53.519 --> 23:55.477
has been conspiring against him.

23:55.521 --> 23:59.176
You want to be the man,
you got to beat the man.

23:59.220 --> 24:03.050
If you can do that...

24:03.093 --> 24:05.922
then, hell....

24:05.966 --> 24:08.664
you should be the man.

24:08.708 --> 24:13.190
Spoiler alert --
He ain't the man.

24:13.234 --> 24:16.193
[Choking]

24:16.237 --> 24:17.804
[Grunts]
[Cracking]

24:17.847 --> 24:21.851
And Simon, he wasn't
the only traitor.

24:21.895 --> 24:25.812
Turns out Dwight was working
with the enemy,

24:25.855 --> 24:28.205
so Negan puts Dwight
where he belongs --

24:28.249 --> 24:29.990
back in a cell,

24:30.033 --> 24:32.166
and he shifts his focus
to ending the war

24:32.209 --> 24:33.950
with the help of Eugene.

24:33.994 --> 24:36.213
♪

24:36.257 --> 24:38.520
Here we go.

24:38.564 --> 24:43.438
Time to do something useful
with our pathetic lives.

24:43.482 --> 24:46.354
And now with Negan's army
fully supplied,

24:46.397 --> 24:48.182
they catch Rick in an ambush.

24:48.225 --> 24:51.011
♪

24:51.054 --> 24:52.578
Negan: [Amplified]
Look at that.

24:52.621 --> 24:56.407
Pegged again.
Pegged so very hard.

24:56.451 --> 24:58.018
♪

24:58.061 --> 25:01.891
But there is one loose end
that Negan didn't account for.

25:01.935 --> 25:03.980
♪

25:04.024 --> 25:07.418
3...

25:07.462 --> 25:09.159
2...

25:09.203 --> 25:11.422
♪

25:11.466 --> 25:13.294
...1.

25:13.337 --> 25:14.948
[Gunfire, screaming]

25:14.991 --> 25:15.949
Aah!

25:15.992 --> 25:18.038
Aah!

25:18.081 --> 25:20.170
Goddamn Eugene.

25:20.214 --> 25:25.262
♪

25:25.306 --> 25:26.829
He's running!

25:26.873 --> 25:34.010
♪

25:34.054 --> 25:38.232
♪

25:38.275 --> 25:40.843
[Grunts]
[Coughs]

25:40.887 --> 25:48.851
♪

25:48.895 --> 25:52.855
After all that,
Negan loses the war.

25:52.899 --> 25:57.164
♪

25:57.207 --> 25:58.818
Save him.

25:58.861 --> 26:01.472
♪

26:01.516 --> 26:04.040
No!
Maggie! Maggie!

26:04.084 --> 26:05.868
No, he can't!

26:05.912 --> 26:09.524
No!
No, he killed Glenn!

26:09.568 --> 26:12.440
Morgan: He loses his people

26:12.483 --> 26:14.616
and loses his freedom.

26:14.660 --> 26:16.705
♪

26:16.749 --> 26:18.489
So it turns out
that solitary confinement

26:18.533 --> 26:21.928
is about the worst punishment
ever for someone like Negan,

26:21.971 --> 26:26.106
And he has nothing to lose
but his life,

26:26.149 --> 26:27.803
and he's ready.

26:27.847 --> 26:30.414
♪

26:30.458 --> 26:31.851
[Door closes]

26:33.374 --> 26:37.247
[Sighs]

26:37.291 --> 26:38.901
Get to it.

26:38.945 --> 26:41.730
Have your justice.

26:41.774 --> 26:44.515
Kill me.

26:44.559 --> 26:46.866
It was worth it.

26:46.909 --> 26:54.482
♪

26:54.525 --> 26:56.092
♪

26:56.136 --> 26:58.268
[Coughing]

26:58.312 --> 27:01.532
♪

27:01.576 --> 27:04.361
Please. Please.

27:04.405 --> 27:06.320
Please kill me.

27:06.363 --> 27:08.452
When Maggie refuses...

27:08.496 --> 27:13.370
I came to kill Negan.

27:13.414 --> 27:15.721
And you're already
worse than dead.

27:15.764 --> 27:18.332
♪

27:18.375 --> 27:19.899
That settles it.

27:19.942 --> 27:21.944
♪

27:21.988 --> 27:23.119
Go.

27:23.163 --> 27:26.732
[Grunting]

27:26.775 --> 27:30.561
♪

27:30.605 --> 27:32.781
As the years went by,
with Rick gone,

27:32.825 --> 27:35.218
Maggie's left,
Negan starts making friends

27:35.262 --> 27:37.394
in the most unlikely places.

27:37.438 --> 27:41.747
"If airplane A is flying east
at 500 miles per hour

27:41.790 --> 27:43.923
and airplane B is flying west

27:43.966 --> 27:47.578
at 650 miles per hour,
how..."
You know what?

27:47.622 --> 27:49.232
You ever seen
an airplane fly

27:49.276 --> 27:52.192
in any direction
at any speed?

27:52.235 --> 27:53.759
No.

27:53.802 --> 27:55.891
Do you think you ever will?

27:58.415 --> 27:59.678
Probably not.

27:59.721 --> 28:02.376
So what the hell difference
does it make?

28:02.419 --> 28:07.990
So even though Negan is making
connections in Alexandria,

28:08.034 --> 28:10.732
he's still looking
for a way out.

28:10.776 --> 28:16.782
♪

28:16.825 --> 28:19.654
Judith: Thought
you were smarter than this.

28:19.698 --> 28:22.352
You know, there's nothing
out there for you.

28:22.396 --> 28:25.181
For anyone.

28:25.225 --> 28:27.009
I promise you

28:27.053 --> 28:29.142
that I'm not gonna hurt
anyone,

28:29.185 --> 28:32.406
even if they try
to hurt me.

28:32.449 --> 28:33.929
I gotta go.

28:33.973 --> 28:36.889
♪

28:36.932 --> 28:39.195
But if I see you again,
I'll shoot.

28:39.239 --> 28:42.155
♪

28:42.198 --> 28:45.941
[Whistling]

28:45.985 --> 28:49.379
♪

28:49.423 --> 28:54.645
But unlike her daddy, Rick,
Judith knows a thing or two.

28:54.689 --> 28:56.430
[Motorcycle approaching]

29:03.916 --> 29:07.484
I told you
there was nothing out there.

29:07.528 --> 29:09.965
You sure as shit did.

29:10.009 --> 29:13.490
Language!
I'm a kid, asshole.

29:13.534 --> 29:17.494
What can I say? I like to swear
in front of my friends.

29:17.538 --> 29:20.628
People that know some shit.

29:20.671 --> 29:22.543
His time in the cell
doesn't last long

29:22.586 --> 29:25.807
when a blizzard strikes and
everyone is forced to evacuate.

29:25.851 --> 29:28.288
♪

29:28.331 --> 29:31.073
[Wind howling]

29:31.117 --> 29:32.901
Now, lucky for them,
they bring him along

29:32.945 --> 29:35.817
because things
go sideways real quick.

29:37.340 --> 29:39.125
Wait!

29:39.168 --> 29:41.127
Judith!

29:43.085 --> 29:45.261
Judith![Dog barking]

29:47.350 --> 29:49.918
[Grunts]
Okay.

29:49.962 --> 29:53.704
[Grunts]
I got you, I got you.

29:53.748 --> 29:55.881
You know, it turns out that
there are some perks

29:55.924 --> 29:57.360
for good behavior.

29:57.404 --> 29:59.188
He gets time out of his cell

29:59.232 --> 30:03.802
and, well, he starts taking
another kid under his wing.

30:03.845 --> 30:06.239
You looking for a job,
kid?

30:06.282 --> 30:09.546
Gage and his friends
started again today.

30:09.590 --> 30:13.289
Again? Jesus.
Alright, kid, look.

30:13.333 --> 30:14.900
Obviously
you're having a day,

30:14.943 --> 30:17.772
but you know what happened
with rolling with it?

30:17.816 --> 30:21.123
I'm not just gonna smile
and take it.
Look.

30:21.167 --> 30:23.386
They are trying
to get a reaction out of you.

30:23.430 --> 30:24.605
They want to see you
upset.

30:24.648 --> 30:26.781
Don't give that to them.
Screw them.

30:26.825 --> 30:30.089
But Lydia's bullies,
they didn't back off.

30:30.132 --> 30:32.526
Shh.

30:32.569 --> 30:34.093
[Exhales shakily]

30:34.136 --> 30:36.573
♪

30:36.617 --> 30:38.749
[Both grunting]Please!

30:38.793 --> 30:44.103
[Straining, whimpering]

30:44.146 --> 30:48.498
♪

30:48.542 --> 30:50.283
Morgan:
So Negan stepped in.

30:50.326 --> 30:53.416
♪

30:53.460 --> 30:55.984
[Crying]

30:56.028 --> 31:00.162
What the hell's going on
back here?Boy: Holy shit. Margo?
Margo?

31:00.206 --> 31:07.169
♪

31:07.213 --> 31:08.605
You know, the people out there
are talking about

31:08.649 --> 31:10.303
putting you down.

31:10.346 --> 31:13.175
Saying Rick ain't around
to save you no more.

31:13.219 --> 31:15.656
Maybe they should have
done it a long time ago.

31:15.699 --> 31:19.790
But just when it seems like
Negan's number is finally up,

31:19.834 --> 31:22.402
he's given a second chance.

31:22.445 --> 31:25.666
A new group called the
Whisperers have started a war

31:25.709 --> 31:26.972
and their leader, Alpha,

31:27.015 --> 31:30.932
she has pissed off
the wrong woman.

31:30.976 --> 31:32.542
Carol: I need this done.

31:32.586 --> 31:37.765
And it'll help every man,
woman and child here.

31:37.808 --> 31:40.072
And what do I
get out of it?

31:40.115 --> 31:43.336
You've been eating
whatever shit we throw your way,

31:43.379 --> 31:47.427
hoping that one day
they'll all forget.

31:47.470 --> 31:50.430
They won't.

31:50.473 --> 31:53.389
Not unless you do something
to make them forget.

31:56.001 --> 31:58.351
So you bring me
Alpha's head.

31:58.394 --> 32:01.876
♪

32:01.920 --> 32:03.878
[Walkers growling]

32:03.922 --> 32:06.968
And with that,
Negan's a free man.

32:07.012 --> 32:11.625
♪

32:11.668 --> 32:13.409
And only he and Carol
know the mission.

32:13.453 --> 32:17.022
♪

32:17.065 --> 32:19.285
[Grunts, groans]

32:19.328 --> 32:24.072
So, now he just has to
convince them to trust him.

32:24.116 --> 32:26.945
Honestly, fellas, what do you
got going on down low?

32:26.988 --> 32:28.468
Are you flyin' around
commando-style,

32:28.511 --> 32:31.862
or do you got, like,
walker long johns with the la--

32:31.906 --> 32:32.994
flap.

32:35.649 --> 32:37.825
[Breathing heavily]Hey, I'm Negan.

32:37.868 --> 32:40.828
♪

32:40.871 --> 32:42.177
For the last eight years,

32:42.221 --> 32:46.703
I have been locked up
by your enemy.

32:46.747 --> 32:48.488
So you take me
to your leader,

32:48.531 --> 32:52.448
and I will spill every
goddamn secret I know.

32:52.492 --> 32:56.539
♪

32:56.583 --> 32:58.324
But see, it's clear
from the jump

32:58.367 --> 33:01.849
that ol' Frown-y McTwoKnives
is threatened by him.

33:01.892 --> 33:03.894
You are a waste.

33:06.027 --> 33:08.856
But Alpha, she quickly
takes a liking to Negan.

33:08.899 --> 33:10.814
And who can blame her?

33:10.858 --> 33:15.254
♪

33:17.778 --> 33:20.085
I'm all in.

33:20.128 --> 33:22.304
Whatever you want,

33:22.348 --> 33:24.654
whatever I got...

33:24.698 --> 33:26.352
it's yours.

33:29.355 --> 33:32.923
♪

33:32.967 --> 33:36.536
I thought you wanted them
to join us.

33:36.579 --> 33:37.711
They will.

33:37.754 --> 33:40.105
♪

33:40.148 --> 33:43.151
As part of my horde.

33:43.195 --> 33:46.937
After the destruction
of Hilltop,

33:46.981 --> 33:48.852
everything comes to a head

33:48.896 --> 33:50.724
when he spots Lydia.

33:50.767 --> 33:53.335
♪

33:53.379 --> 33:55.511
[Gasps]

33:55.555 --> 33:57.513
Stop.

33:57.557 --> 33:58.993
Sorry, kid.

33:59.037 --> 34:00.690
This shit is done.

34:01.996 --> 34:03.519
Alpha.

34:08.655 --> 34:11.527
Thing you've been looking for?

34:11.571 --> 34:13.486
I found it.

34:13.529 --> 34:18.360
He promised Alpha
that he would find her daughter.

34:18.404 --> 34:20.710
And as he leads her to Lydia,

34:20.754 --> 34:25.150
he tries to find any remaining
trace of Alpha's humanity.

34:25.193 --> 34:27.152
You think that
it makes you strong

34:27.195 --> 34:32.200
to say that emotions aren't
real, that we are animals?

34:32.244 --> 34:36.248
That is bullshit,
and you know it.

34:36.291 --> 34:40.078
And now you claim that you have
to kill your own daughter,

34:40.121 --> 34:42.341
your own
flesh and blood.

34:42.384 --> 34:45.605
♪

34:45.648 --> 34:47.563
It is her destiny.

34:47.607 --> 34:53.874
♪

34:53.917 --> 34:55.789
He won't let anyone hurt Lydia.

34:55.832 --> 35:00.794
♪

35:00.837 --> 35:06.016
♪

35:08.236 --> 35:10.847
[Sputters]

35:10.891 --> 35:12.588
[Gasps]

35:19.682 --> 35:22.120
[Growling]

35:25.558 --> 35:28.213
Took you long enough.

35:28.256 --> 35:31.216
Everyone's a critic.

35:31.259 --> 35:34.523
[Growling]

35:34.567 --> 35:37.396
♪

35:37.439 --> 35:39.659
Negan:
Is this what you wanted?

35:39.702 --> 35:42.836
What took you
so damn long?

35:42.879 --> 35:44.272
I told you to do it fast.

35:44.316 --> 35:46.187
It's done.

35:46.231 --> 35:47.580
Alright, I held up my end.

35:47.623 --> 35:50.887
Now I'm asking you
to hold up yours.

35:50.931 --> 35:52.498
Just walk me
through those gates

35:52.541 --> 35:56.850
so I can open up a new chapter
in the book of Negan.

35:56.893 --> 36:00.636
I'm not going back.

36:00.680 --> 36:02.203
Not yet.

36:02.247 --> 36:04.684
♪

36:04.727 --> 36:08.166
The disappointments continue
when he goes to release Lydia.

36:09.558 --> 36:12.692
Hey, kid, I'm sorry about...

36:12.735 --> 36:14.084
Shit.

36:14.128 --> 36:15.260
Oh!

36:15.303 --> 36:17.523
God!Where's Alpha?!

36:17.566 --> 36:20.656
Look,
whatever Lydia told you --Where is she?!

36:20.700 --> 36:22.702
She is dead.

36:22.745 --> 36:24.921
She is dead.
I killed her.

36:24.965 --> 36:26.532
You liar.

36:26.575 --> 36:28.490
See, now, Negan knows
that Daryl's not going

36:28.534 --> 36:33.147
to take his word for it,
so he shows him the evidence.

36:33.191 --> 36:36.672
I swear to God
it was on that spike.

36:36.716 --> 36:40.154
Look, we -- we sit here
and we wait for Carol

36:40.198 --> 36:41.547
or I can take you
to find the --

36:41.590 --> 36:44.245
Oh, come on, man.

36:44.289 --> 36:47.161
We're talking
about Lydia here.

36:47.205 --> 36:48.728
Why would I stash her
out banjo country

36:48.771 --> 36:50.773
unless the whole point
was to keep her safe,

36:50.817 --> 36:53.776
unless the whole frickin' point
was just to use her as bait

36:53.820 --> 36:55.474
so I could get Alpha alone?

36:55.517 --> 36:57.867
You sure took your sweet ass
time, though, didn't you?

36:57.911 --> 37:00.696
What is with you guys thinking
I didn't do it fast enough?

37:00.740 --> 37:06.963
♪

37:07.007 --> 37:09.531
Alpha's dead...

37:09.575 --> 37:12.273
because of you.

37:12.317 --> 37:14.101
We kneel...

37:14.144 --> 37:15.624
to the new Alpha.

37:15.668 --> 37:20.368
♪

37:20.412 --> 37:23.241
You should
probably shoot me.

37:23.284 --> 37:25.286
Don't threaten me
with a good time.

37:25.330 --> 37:27.941
♪

37:27.984 --> 37:29.159
Shit.

37:29.203 --> 37:31.510
[All grunting]

37:31.553 --> 37:36.732
♪

37:39.431 --> 37:44.523
Now that Daryl believes Negan,
they rejoin the group.

37:44.566 --> 37:47.352
And with Alpha's number two
still out for revenge...

37:47.395 --> 37:49.789
Negan: [Whispering]
Hey, shit head.

37:49.832 --> 37:51.747
...he takes it
upon himself to end things.

37:51.791 --> 37:54.402
♪

37:54.446 --> 37:56.361
[Walkers growling]

37:56.404 --> 38:01.322
♪

38:01.366 --> 38:04.238
[Both grunting]

38:04.282 --> 38:06.545
For Alpha.

38:06.588 --> 38:13.291
♪

38:13.334 --> 38:15.249
So with the skin freaks
out of the picture,

38:15.293 --> 38:17.425
Negan starts to think that,

38:17.469 --> 38:21.342
well, maybe he can be
part of this group.

38:21.386 --> 38:24.040
But then...

38:24.084 --> 38:27.261
Maggie returns.

38:27.305 --> 38:28.567
Hi, Maggie.

38:28.610 --> 38:32.658
♪

38:32.701 --> 38:37.227
I didn't escape if
that's what you're thinking.

38:37.271 --> 38:39.534
So now with Maggie back...

38:39.578 --> 38:43.799
♪

38:43.843 --> 38:46.367
...nobody feels comfortable
keeping Negan around.

38:48.674 --> 38:51.677
[Door creaks]

38:51.720 --> 38:54.201
I see you went ahead
and moved me in.

38:54.244 --> 38:57.465
Daryl helped.
I'm sorry.

38:57.509 --> 39:00.599
The council
has voted to banish you.

39:00.642 --> 39:02.905
What you want just...
isn't gonna happen.

39:02.949 --> 39:04.472
It's not possible.

39:04.516 --> 39:07.083
I know it's not
what I promised,

39:07.127 --> 39:10.391
but given our
less recent history...

39:10.435 --> 39:13.873
it's better
than you deserve.

39:13.916 --> 39:17.398
It doesn't matter
that he's not in his cell.

39:17.442 --> 39:20.836
Negan's alone,
completely alone.

39:20.880 --> 39:22.925
♪

39:22.969 --> 39:25.885
Negan: You know what
the sad part is?

39:25.928 --> 39:28.235
That you thought
for even a second

39:28.278 --> 39:29.454
that those folks
would see you

39:29.497 --> 39:32.544
for anything
but who you truly are.

39:34.459 --> 39:36.678
Which is me.

39:36.722 --> 39:39.028
[Glass shatters]

39:40.465 --> 39:42.423
And even digging up Lucille...

39:42.467 --> 39:48.473
♪

39:48.516 --> 39:51.476
Even that's not enough
to keep his demons at bay.

39:51.519 --> 39:56.655
♪

40:00.963 --> 40:05.925
Negan: I am sorry
that I left you.

40:05.968 --> 40:07.535
I was a coward.

40:07.579 --> 40:12.714
I couldn't face the pain
of losing you, so I ran away.

40:12.758 --> 40:16.283
I'm sorry that you went out
like that.

40:16.326 --> 40:18.590
I should've been there.

40:18.633 --> 40:23.638
I am sorry that I named
a stupid baseball bat after you.

40:23.682 --> 40:26.728
♪

40:26.772 --> 40:29.644
I love the shit out of you.

40:29.688 --> 40:32.560
♪

40:32.604 --> 40:35.737
I'm gonna do your fighting
for you.

40:35.781 --> 40:45.530
♪

40:45.573 --> 40:49.011
If you stay here,
she will kill you.

40:49.055 --> 40:53.146
I just didn't want your death
on my conscience, and...

40:53.189 --> 40:54.364
now it's not.

40:54.408 --> 40:56.758
Fair enough.

40:56.802 --> 41:00.501
♪

41:00.545 --> 41:04.287
Morgan: Love him or hate him...

41:04.331 --> 41:07.726
Negan is done running.

41:07.769 --> 41:09.989
Some people might think
he's a villain,

41:10.032 --> 41:13.383
but Negan,
he has a code and he follows it.

41:13.427 --> 41:18.432
Negan: You don't kill people
that don't deserve it...

41:18.476 --> 41:21.130
and you never kill kids.

41:21.174 --> 41:23.785
Right or wrong,

41:23.829 --> 41:28.790
Negan, he does what
he does to survive.

41:28.834 --> 41:33.752
And can you really fault him
for that?

41:33.795 --> 41:38.539
So whatever happens next,
one thing is for certain.

41:38.583 --> 41:40.585
Negan is telling
his own story...

41:40.628 --> 41:44.719
♪

41:44.763 --> 41:45.894
...his way.

41:45.938 --> 41:53.336
♪

41:53.380 --> 41:54.729
[Water dripping]

41:54.773 --> 41:57.558
[Loud, reverberating creaking]

42:00.996 --> 42:03.608
Alden:
What the hell was that?[Dog barks]

42:04.609 --> 42:06.654
[Creaking]

42:06.698 --> 42:08.264
The storm's pushing air
through the pipes,

42:08.308 --> 42:10.049
making them groan.

42:10.092 --> 42:12.051
It's nothing serious.
We're good.

42:12.094 --> 42:15.010
[Creaking]

42:20.102 --> 42:23.453
[Creaking]

42:23.497 --> 42:25.804
Know what that noise
actually is?

42:25.847 --> 42:29.459
That is God,
telling us to turn around.

42:29.503 --> 42:31.636
I'm pretty sure He would have
ran that by me first.

42:31.679 --> 42:33.072
Oh, yeah?

42:33.115 --> 42:37.250
The Good Lord direct
your one eyeball to this?

42:37.293 --> 42:38.904
Water-line mark.

42:39.992 --> 42:42.081
That means this tunnel floods
on a regular basis,

42:42.124 --> 42:43.996
like when it rains.

42:44.039 --> 42:46.041
[Creaking]

42:47.173 --> 42:50.698
It's bad down here.
It's worse up there.

42:50.742 --> 42:52.439
Look, man,
all I am saying --

42:52.482 --> 42:54.528
And it ain't working.

42:54.572 --> 42:56.182
You trying
to run shit.

42:56.225 --> 42:59.011
Keep moving.

42:59.054 --> 43:00.273
Come on.
[Whistles]

43:00.316 --> 43:02.884
Dog!
[Dog barks]

43:02.928 --> 43:05.800
You're in on it.

43:05.844 --> 43:08.803
[Creaking]

43:08.847 --> 43:17.072
♪

43:17.116 --> 43:25.080
♪

43:25.124 --> 43:33.436
♪

43:33.480 --> 43:41.793
♪
